"title": "8810: riches, dangers of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8810: riches, dangers of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Material wealth can be a source of both physical and spiritual danger, against which believers are clearly warned to be on their guard.</p>\n<h2>Riches are spiritually dangerous</h2>\n<h3>Love of riches a root of many evils</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:11\">JOS 7:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:20-Josh7:21\">JOS 7:20–7:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:3\">1TI 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>They may lead to divided loyalty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:24\">MAT 6:24</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:13\">LUK 16:13</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:9-Matt4:10\">MAT 4:9–4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:4\">JAS 4:4</a></p>\n<h3>They may hinder people's response to the gospel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:22\">MAT 13:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:19\">MRK 4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:14\">LUK 8:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21-Matt19:22\">MAT 19:21–19:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:21-Mark10:22\">MRK 10:21–10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:22-Luke18:23\">LUK 18:22–18:23</a></p>\n<h3>They may create false security</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:24-Job31:28\">JOB 31:24–31:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:6-Ps52:7\">PSA 52:6–52:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:28\">PRO 11:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:4\">JER 49:4</a></p>\n<h3>They may make people proud</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:5\">EZK 28:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:10\">PSA 62:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:23\">PRO 18:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:11\">PRO 28:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:8\">HOS 12:8</a></p>\n<h3>They may cause unbelief and anxiety</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:12\">ECC 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:17-Job20:20\">JOB 20:17–20:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:6\">PRO 15:6</a></p>\n<h3>They may lead people to forget God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:8-Prov30:9\">PRO 30:8–30:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:10-Deut8:14\">DEU 8:10–8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:15\">DEU 32:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:25-Neh9:26\">NEH 9:25–9:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:6\">HOS 13:6</a></p>\n<h2>Riches are physically dangerous</h2>\n<h3>Working for them may cause excessive tiredness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:4\">PRO 23:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:26-John6:27\">JHN 6:26–6:27</a></p>\n<h3>Enjoying them may lead to self-indulgence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:5\">JAS 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:3-Hag1:5\">HAG 1:3–1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:25\">MAT 23:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:19-Luke16:21\">LUK 16:19–16:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:8-1Tim6:9\">1TI 6:8–6:9</a></p>\n<h3>Misusing them may foster oppression and injustice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:13\">LEV 19:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:12-Deut24:15\">DEU 24:12–24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:16\">PRO 22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:23\">ISA 1:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:13\">JER 22:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:12\">MIC 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">MAL 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:6\">JAS 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:4\">JAS 5:4</a></p>",
